summary: EUR Card incoming payments show systematic underpayment from February through July 2025. Contract rate is 3.8% but reconciliation shows effective rates of 3.50-3.64%. Total underpayment: 133,419.09 EUR across 6 months.

notes.text: Effective rate consistently ~3.5% across all 6 months, significantly below the 3.8% contract rate. This represents a systematic gap, not a one-time discrepancy.
January 2025 and all 2024 months show rates close to 3.8% (within noise threshold). The discrepancy begins in February 2025.
February shows a transitional rate of 3.64%, while March-July stabilize around 3.50%. This suggests a rate configuration change occurred in early February.
